Hello,

I have found Marine Clean to be a very good degreaser.
It is sold on www.por15.com

 Lacaur thinner also works well to wipe away sticky
residue. Most of the time, I use a wire brush on my
drill to remove weather strip glue. This is the
fastest method I think.

Good Luck!

David Kelly
From Wilmington, NC

